z. Mindegyik oszlop tartalmazza a legfelső szintű oldal nevét, alatta az oldal közvetlen utódjával.</Description><Description language-id=\"de_DE\">Zeigt eine Spalte für jede Seite der obersten Ebene. Jede Spalte enthält den Namen einer Seite der obersten Ebene, darunter werden die direkten Unterseiten aufgelistet.</Description></root>','display',NULL,'ftl','<#if entries?has_content>\n	<@liferay_aui.row>\n		<#list entries as entry>\n			<#if (entry.getType() != \"asset_display\") && (getterUtil.getBoolean(showHiddenPages) || !entry.isHidden()) && layoutPermission.containsWithoutViewableGroup(permissionChecker, entry, \"VIEW\")>\n				<@liferay_aui.col width=25>\n					<div class=\"results-header\">\n						<h3>\n							<a\n\n							<#assign layoutType = entry.getLayoutType() />\n\n							<#if layoutType.isBrowsable()>\n								href=\"${portalUtil.getLayoutURL(entry, themeDisplay)}\"\n							</#if>\n\n							>${entry.getName(locale)}</a>\n						</h3>\n					</div>\n\n					<@displayPages\n						depth=1\n						pages=entry.getChildren(permissionChecker)\n					/>\n				</@liferay_aui.col>\n			</#if>\n		</#list>\n	</@liferay_aui.row>\n</#if>\n\n<#macro displayPages\n	depth\n	pages\n>\n	<#if pages?has_content && ((depth < displayDepth?number) || (displayDepth?number == 0))>\n		<ul class=\"child-pages\">\n			<#list pages as page>\n				<#if (page.getType() != \"asset_display\") && (getterUtil.getBoolean(showHiddenPages) || !page.isHidden())>\n					<li>\n						<a\n\n						<#assign pageType = page.getLayoutType() />\n\n						<#if pageType.isBrowsable()>\n							href=\"${portalUtil.getLayoutURL(page, themeDisplay)}\"\n						</#if>\n\n						>${page.getName(locale)}</a>\n\n						<@displayPages\n							depth=depth + 1\n							pages=page.getChildren(permissionChecker)\n						/>\n					</li>\n				</#if>\n			</#list>\n		</ul>\n	</#if>\n</#macro>',0,0,34705,NULL,NULL),('da559c01-26d3-68c7-5601-88c3d26e11d7',34707,34470,34422,34425,NULL,34425,NULL,'2021-05-19 08:43:22.356000','2021-05-19 08:4